<body class="article-page">

  <div class="disclosure-bar">
    Independent reviews — affiliate links at no extra cost to you.&nbsp;
    <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Full disclosure</a>&nbsp;·&nbsp;
    <a href="/how-we-review/">How we review</a>
  </div>

  <Nav />

  <main>
    <header class="article-header">
      <div class="article-header-cat">Legal</div>
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <div class="article-header-meta">
        <span>Last updated: April 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>Stack and Sleep participates in affiliate marketing programmes. This means we earn a commission when you click on certain links and make a purchase — at no additional cost to you.</p>

      <h2>How affiliate links work</h2>
      <p>When you click a product link on this site and subsequently purchase the product, we may receive a small commission from the retailer or brand. The price you pay is exactly the same whether you use our link or go directly to the retailer.</p>

      <h2>Programmes we participate in</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — We earn from qualifying purchases as an Amazon Associate.</li>
        <li><strong>Impact.com</strong> — Affiliate network covering Oura Ring, Eight Sleep, AG1, Momentous, and others.</li>
        <li><strong>ShareASale</strong> — Affiliate network covering Thorne, Hatch, and others.</li>
        <li><strong>Direct programmes</strong> — We may participate in direct affiliate programmes from brands including Joovv, Plunge, and Sunlighten.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our editorial independence</h2>
      <p>Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial judgements. We recommend products based on their merit — not their commission rate. If a product isn't worth buying, we say so, even if it pays a higher commission than our top pick.</p>

      <p>We do not accept payment for positive reviews, sponsored rankings, or editorial coverage. All sponsored content, if any, will be clearly labelled.</p>

      <h2>FTC compliance</h2>
      <p>In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's guidelines on endorsements and testimonials, we disclose our affiliate relationships on every page of this site and in any content where affiliate links appear.</p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
